		name = "CTRL+N"
		command = "CreateCharacter"
	elem 
		name = "Numpad5"
		command = "testVerb"
	elem 
		name = "F1"
		command = ".options"

macro "macro"
	elem 
		name = "Tab"
		command = "Action-Verb"
